er\" class=\"annual-card\">\n    <div class=\"annual-icon\">📊</div>\n    <div class=\"annual-content\">\n      <strong>ANNUAL REPORT - 2018-19</strong>\n    </div>\n    <span class=\"annual-arrow\">→</span>\n  </a>\n  \n  <a href=\"https://mcf.indianrailways.gov.in/works/uploads/File/Annual%20Report%202017-18.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"annual-card\">\n    <div class=\"annual-icon\">📊</div>\n    <div class=\"annual-content\">\n      <strong>ANNUAL REPORT - 2017-18</strong>\n    </div>\n    <span class=\"annual-arrow\">→</span>\n  </a>\n  \n  <a href=\"https://mcf.indianrailways.gov.in/works/uploads/File/Annual%20Report%202016-17.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"annual-card\">\n    <div class=\"annual-icon\">📊</div>\n    <div class=\"annual-content\">\n      <strong>ANNUAL REPORT - 2016-17</strong>\n    </div>\n    <span class=\"annual-arrow\">→</span>\n  </a>\n  \n  <a href=\"https://mcf.indianrailways.gov.in/works/uploads/File/Final%20AR%202015-16(4).pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"annual-card\">\n    <div class=\"annual-icon\">📊</div>\n    <div class=\"annual-content\">\n      <strong>ANNUAL REPORT - 2015-16</strong>\n    </div>\n    <span class=\"annual-arrow\">→</span>\n  </a>\n</div>",
